title: Welcome to Brighton North in Shoreline! Large 2 Bedroom Apartment
posting_body: ['Brighton North Apartments are located is located in the in the beautiful city of Shoreline, WA.', 'One of the most desirable residential neighborhoods north of Seattle, with convenient access to downtown Seattle.', 'Nearby stores, shopping, and major retail, grocery stores, restaurants.', 'The schools are some of the best in the area, the award-winning Shoreline School District.', 'Nearby parks and the Shoreline public library are a few minutes away.', 'Building Amenities:', '-Close to I-5 and the soon to be 175th Street light rail station.', '- Parking Garage', '-On-site Management & Maintenance', '-After-hours Emergency Services', '-Secured Access Building', '-Pet Friendly Cats only', '-On-line Payments', '-Quick Access to I-5, I-405, and HWY 99', '-Easy Walking Distance to grocery, banks, Bus lines, Light Rail Station, Shopping, Dining, Nightlife, Shoreline Library.', '--Parcel Acceptance', '*Large living room & Dinning Area', '*Beautiful Fireplace', '*Great Location (Near I-5)', '*Parking Included', '*Walk-In Closet', '*Small Private Balcony', '*Secure Access', 'Move in Costs', '$40.00 per person application fee over the age of 18', '$1000.00 Refundable Deposit', 'Pet deposit required', 'Flat rate utility charge for W,S,& G $70 for one person/ $140 for two', 'Tenant pays for own electricity', 'Please contact Patrick @', 'show contact info']
